{"tid":2322612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前TVB新聞小花梁凱寧公開童年絕密照 網民大讚：好似混血兒","createTime":"2020-12-12T12:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T13:46:30.000Z","uid":77400,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f88edb0a380d47932398803c5a9526e0257853","tid":2322612,"uid":77400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"28歲前TVB新聞主播梁凱寧去年9月離開工作了6年的TVB新聞台後，變成了自由身仍工作不斷，人氣一直不減，儲落好多粉絲。近日她公開了童年絕密照，發現Maggie細個已是一個美人胚子。<br />\n<br />\n梁凱寧近日在IG分享童年照，以及與哥哥、家人的舊照片，表示：「抗疫期間多咗時間同屋企人留喺屋企，前幾日就同屋企人一齊睇舊相，跟住發現我爸爸媽媽真係好靚仔靚女。」<br />\n<br />\n當中最吸睛嘅就係佢張童年照，年紀細細已經係美人胚子，下巴尖尖笑容甜美，仲有啲鬼鬼哋，網民都問佢係咪混血，全家都似外國人咁話！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7by1w8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7by1w8O.jpg&h=d4cc366a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n媾死仔喇～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2UTofS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2UTofS.jpg&h=e4d4e1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfZ4uVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfZ4uVU.jpg&h=81e1d9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Nd8WA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Nd8WA1.jpg&h=46b7a8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p16202M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp16202M.jpg&h=3480ef5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbSxDPu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbSxDPu.jpg&h=6ecc7799&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYZHgBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYZHgBd.jpg&h=cb408b65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xj0bUnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXj0bUnV.jpg&h=3104298d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFma9Wm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k